{"type": "article", "id": 33532, "title": "家里地方小，那就把床头柜挂在床边上？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-20T23:05:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 9999, "name": "Flos"}, {"id": 34146, "name": "MB&F"}, {"id": 34147, "name": "Caran d’Ache"}, {"id": 34159, "name": "Twentyfive"}, {"id": 34148, "name": "ArmsReach Industries"}, {"id": 34149, "name": "Vicent Van Duysen"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 187, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161021065919Z02JoEB9uSF1LIcV.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>          </p><h3>Night Caddy by ArmsReach Industries</h3><p>          </p><p>还在费心怎么在小户型的卧室塞进一个床头柜吗？最近来自美国的 <a href=\"http://armsreachind.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">ArmsReach Industries</a> 公司就提供了一种新的收纳方式，这个名叫 Night Caddy 收纳架可以根据需要悬挂在床架或是席梦思上，让你能够更整洁有序地放置眼镜、耳机、水杯等物品。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1664464034/night-caddy-the-new-age-nightstand\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 31 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020170628eJpyaVc4UNv6GkAb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.594118\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016102017062858qQKjGE0zDnOZhL.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610201706287Yxg0y5em19sMPoO.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020170628eqPH5wbEulFY63NI.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560294\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020170628FhupQZN4G7JVCjx2.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558824\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Casting by Vicent Van Duysen</h3><p>          </p><p>在比利时科特赖克室内设计双年展上，设计师 <a href=\"http://vincentvanduysen.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vicent Van Duysen</a> 展出了自己为意大利品牌 <a href=\"http://www.flos.com/en/home\" rel=\"nofollow\">Flos</a> 设计的一套户外灯饰 Casting 系列。这些灯饰的造型看上去就像是字母 C 和 T 的雕塑作品，由混凝土和铸铁等材料制作而成，表面则经过镀铝处理，适用于花园、人行道等户外场所。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020170646Zc9GEUyA5qpIdaC4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020170646qauEm0HwjXy7crKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020170644VXtifWYwTbdR8D24.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020170644qkv7VewifLp6COKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020170644TZznsBKYO5JvoMGS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Astrograph by MB&amp;F &amp; Caran d’Ache</h3><p>          </p><p>如果你和瑞士创意机构 <a href=\"https://www.mbandf.com/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">MB&amp;F</a> 的创始人 Maximilian Büsser 一样，曾梦想过在宇宙中漫游并一直对航天飞船抱有热情的话，你或许能体会到这款 Astrograph 签字笔的魅力。这些细节上充满了航天元素的签字笔由 MB&amp;F 和制笔厂 <a href=\"http://www.carandache.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Caran d’Ache</a> 花费四年时间共同打造，试图最大程度地还原出一艘真正的飞船。每一支笔都由 99 个零件组装而成， 你会发现伸展自如的起落架、微型梯子和一名宇航员。<a href=\"https://www.mbandf.com/en/machines/co-creations/astrograph\" rel=\"nofollow\">Astrograph</a> 一共有四种款式，每款限量 99 个。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020174847tfCSiDIV1oW7Lz0U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.727083\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020174847go5q1y8FS9xGNdiA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.727083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610201748470PcZRvLA46QTex9r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.727083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020174848ktWMLIunENbqKOjS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><p>          </p><h3>Ebba Chair by Adam Lewandowicz</h3><p>          </p><p><a href=\"https://www.behance.net/adam_lewandowicz\" rel=\"nofollow\">Adam Lewandowicz</a> 是一名就读于美国辛辛那提大学工业设计系的学生，这张名为 Ebba 的椅子是他花费三个半月打造的一个设计项目。虽然椅子的外形相当简洁低调，但它的细节却非常抢眼：两边的扶手仿佛是底座的延续，在座位下交错后产生了奇特的视觉效果，让人联想到莫乌比斯带。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020181847NyVqjD2ewiFnBTGo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.470833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020181847dVTGU4st2O5cangX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.470833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020181847Kh4Qo2qMOiNTeBDH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.470833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Matchbox Card by Shop3xu</h3><p>          </p><p>想用更有创意的方式告白或是送去祝福的话，不妨试试这些由越南工作室 <a href=\"http://www.shop3xu.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shop3xu</a> 手工制作的火柴盒。和纸质贺卡不同的是，拉出盒子的动作让那些充满趣味的暖心祝福多了一种惊喜感。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/3xudesign\" rel=\"nofollow\">网店链接</a>，你还可以在它的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/shop3xu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> 上看到更多实物图。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020182610SOAYJ0cHM4PkdeVo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610201826107SU1RqjDX6uoTlpF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772368\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020182610VQRdcM6yTqUrAHFI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020182610WJV4Xywrcq3AEfjF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610201826102rDenhuZcvswQWE3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Yōjōki by Twentyfive</h3><p>          </p><p>阿根廷创意机构 <a href=\"http://betwentyfive.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Twnetyfive</a> 最近接到委托，为日本茶叶品牌设计一套形象。设计师们从写于 1211 年的古书《喫茶養生記》（Kissa Yōjōki）中汲取灵感，不仅借书名确定了品牌名称，还为三款茶叶搭配了简洁清新的插图。与之形成鲜明对比的是极简的大礼盒，黑白两色加上镀金，并没有其他额外的修饰，体现出低调奢华的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020203750CdfzOotYgXyGRnUB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020203750R2y4LJmcYGCVfsti.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593023\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016102020375065FLWiafXtMhTVrS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593023\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020203751q4bzcQgZY9EupMBo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593023\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161020203751ST5uxhOnAytH8iUV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593023\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}